
Ranger Help for: lake
=====================

SUMMARY:    
The lake is similar to the sea, but smaller in size and usually made up
of fresh water. All sorts of fish live in lakes, and while it is good
source of food, no Rangers line in a lake. Lots of times, Rangers will
live near them though. Ranger skills use in limited in lakes. Lakes can
be found on most all of the continents.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: Individual terrains

